poldek test suite

BuildRequires: check-devel
Reqires: fakeroot

To run all tests:

$ make check        # runs all tests
$ ./run-sh-tests.sh # runs tests written in shell only (sh/ subdir)


sh/ test scripts may be executed separately:

$ ./sh/07-depsolver -h

Particular tests may be choosen:

$ ./sh/07-depsolver -v -t testSuggests
